S. O. BEREN v. O. G. COULTER et al. No. 4861. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. June 22, 1954. Jochems, Sargent & Blaes, Wichita, Kan., and McKay & McKay, El Dorado, Kan., for appellant. Blackburn & Hampton, Great Bend, Kan., and Depew, Stanley, Weigand, Hook & Curfman, Wichita, Kan., for ap-pellees.

Before PHILLIPS, Chief Judge, and BRATTON and HUXMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed on motion of appellant.
